org.apache.river.mahalo.proxy

Class TxnMgrProxy

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.river.mahalo.proxy.TxnMgrProxy
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Remote, Administrable, net.jini.core.transaction.server.TransactionConstants, net.jini.core.transaction.server.TransactionManager, net.jini.export.ProxyAccessor, net.jini.id.ReferentUuid

    public class TxnMgrProxy
extends Object
implements net.jini.core.transaction.server.TransactionManager, Administrable, Serializable, net.jini.id.ReferentUuid, net.jini.export.ProxyAccessor
    A TxnMgrProxy is a proxy for the transaction manager service. This is the object passed to clients of this service. It implements the TransactionManager and the Administrable interfaces.
    Since:
    1.1
    Author:
    Sun Microsystems, Inc.
